{"id": "1518888370527408218", "channel_id": "1518888370527408218", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "**V2.5.2 沉渊**\n\n深渊比灾难更早地找上了他，\n他的一生也没有第二种选择。\n古老的猎哨声响彻海岸线，\n穷途末路的他，终于得以留存一切。\n\n不会再有任何东西能够脱离他的掌控。\n不会再有任何事物能够让他面对分离。\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\n**V2.5.2 What the Abyss Keeps**\n\nThe abyss came for him before catastrophe could. He was never going to have another choice. \nThe ancient hunting whistle rang out down the coastline. He had nowhere left to run—and only then, he could at last keep them all. Every last one. Forever.\n\nNever again will anything slip beyond his control. \nNever again will anyone be torn from his side.\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\n**V2.5.2 심연**\n\n심연은 재앙보다 먼저 그를 찾아왔고,\n그의 일생에는 두 번째 선택이 없었다.\n고대의 사냥 호각 소리가 해안선을 울리고,\n궁지에 몰린 그는, 마침내 모든 것을 붙잡을 수 있었다.\n\n더 이상 어떤 것도 그의 통제를 벗어날 수 없으리라.\n더 이상 어떤 것도 그로 하여금 이별을 맞이하게 하지 못하리라.", "timestamp": "2026-06-23T08:00:07.115000+00:00", "pinned": true, "thread_id": "1518888370527408218", "reactions": [{"emoji": "Leigh_wow", "emoji_id": "1356053147029864518", "count": 46}, {"emoji": "What", "emoji_id": "1356085150869622965", "count": 7}, {"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}, {"emoji": "🫃", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1518888370963746909", "filename": "Pontos.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3629224, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1518888370527408218/1518888370963746909/Pontos.png?ex=6a3c3747&is=6a3ae5c7&hm=bade3110e525cb6bb04acee391adaca3bea65e8e85fff5681f895d89e2f64c40&"}]}
